                                    name: 'p2_processControl',
                                    class: 'lead',
                                    value: 'Easily manage variability and high mix process control with MIP. Our system intuitively reacts to the individual components and options of the BOM without the need to configure every possible variant of the product.'
                                })

                    .row.mb-4
                        .col
                            h3.text-uppercase
                                +rawHtml ({
                                    name: 'h3_processControl',
                                    value: 'Connect any IoT Devices.'
                                })

                            p.lead
                                +rawHtml ({
                                    name: 'p3_processControl',
                                    class: 'lead',
                                    value: 'No code necessary. Automatically display the correct build option, associated work instruction, and device controls based on BOM or Model at the station level.'
                                })
                    
                    .row
                        .col
                            h3.text-uppercase
                                +rawHtml ({
                                    name: 'h4_processControl',
                                    value: 'Adjust Process Controls Anytime.'
                                })

                            p.lead
                                +rawHtml ({
                                    name: 'p4_processControl',
                                    class: 'lead',
                                    value: 'MIP Data gives you a high-level overview of the plant floor. Seamlessly rebalance lines with drag-n-drop, adjust process controls, and attune any sudden discrepancies.'
                                })
        
    //- Platform Capabiltiies
    .container.py-3
        .p-3.p-md-5
            .row.align-items-center.mb-5
                .col-12.col-lg-6
                    h2.display-1.text-uppercase.text-break.text-lg-nowrap.mb-4
                        +rawHtml ({
                            name: 'heading_capabilities',
                            value: 'Modular & Agile Solutions'
                        })

                    p.lead
                        +rawHtml ({
                            name: 'p1_capabilities',
                            value: 'It’s one integrated platform. It’s all connected so it doesn’t need months to configure. You can be up and running in just a few days. No more complex layers— no more vendors trying to talk to each other across your manufacturing environment.'
                        })

            //- Capabilities - Work Instructions
            .row.no-gutters
                .col-12.col-lg-6
                    +card ({
                        name: 'card1',
                        title: 'Work Instructions',
                        icon: 'fas fa-chart-bar text-primary',
                        subTitle: 'Paperless Factory'
                    })
    
                .col-12.col-lg-6
                    .row.no-gutters
                        .col-12.col-lg
                            +card ({
                                name: 'card2',
                                src: 'https://picsum.photos/400/200',
